Some installation images of ‘The Painted Room’ which is now open @grimmgallery in Amsterdam until 22nd December. I was very happy to see how these paintings of interiors sat in the space of Grimm’s canal house gallery with its panelling, fire places and nods to domesticity. The relationship of the many windows represented in the paintings with the many windows in the gallery was particularly satisfying to see. 
Big thanks to all the artists for sending such great paintings-

